<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 20:07:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯被囚禁100天：以色列人质家属必须发动自己的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-14/ty-article/.highlight/100-days-in-hamas-captivity-israeli-hostages-families-must-wage-their-own-war/0000018d-08c1-daa5-a7cf-dee332850000</link><description>当仍被扣押在加沙的 136 名人质迎来被囚禁一百天之际，他们的亲属正在考虑必须继续战斗，谁知道他们的困境还要持续多久才能成为公众关注的焦点</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 18:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-14/ty-article/.highlight/100-days-in-hamas-captivity-israeli-hostages-families-must-wage-their-own-war/0000018d-08c1-daa5-a7cf-dee332850000</guid></item><item><title>战争爆发时，我们与这些加沙人进行了交谈。这就是他们所经历的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-talked-with-these-gazans-when-the-war-broke-this-is-where-they-are-now/0000018d-0870-d8a7-a1df-aefef6540000</link><description>《国土报》重新采访了四名加沙人，他们在战争刚开始时就谈到了战争，发现他们流离失所、遭到轰炸，挤在狭小的地区，同时努力寻求医疗救助，并感到死亡即将来临</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-talked-with-these-gazans-when-the-war-broke-this-is-where-they-are-now/0000018d-0870-d8a7-a1df-aefef6540000</guid></item><item><title>真主党导弹杀死以色列妇女及其儿子；以色列国防军击毙三名渗透黎巴嫩边境的恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-missile-kills-two-israelis-idf-kills-terrorists-infiltrating-lebanon-border/0000018d-0859-d8a7-a1df-aeffda470000</link><description>以色列军队称袭击了黎巴嫩真主党目标，并下令关闭边境地区的民用交通。 ■ 以色列国防军估计，渗透边境的恐怖分子计划袭击附近的一个基地；巴勒斯坦组织声称对此事负责</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-missile-kills-two-israelis-idf-kills-terrorists-infiltrating-lebanon-border/0000018d-0859-d8a7-a1df-aeffda470000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的高级盟友和顾问因煽动种族主义而被定罪，恐怖指控被无罪释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/top-ben-gvir-ally-and-adviser-convicted-of-inciting-racism-acquitted-of-terror-charges/0000018d-0841-d71c-ad9f-4bc314350000</link><description>极右翼卡汉主义者本茨·戈普斯坦因针对阿拉伯人的言论而被定罪：“我们内部的敌人是癌症。”他因发表美化 1994 年希伯伦大屠杀的种族主义言论而被无罪释放。判决后他说道：“我为我所说的话感到自豪”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/top-ben-gvir-ally-and-adviser-convicted-of-inciting-racism-acquitted-of-terror-charges/0000018d-0841-d71c-ad9f-4bc314350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名周六在加沙地带战斗中丧生的以色列预备役士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-saturday/0000018d-0879-d71c-ad9f-4bfb1dcb0000</link><description>这名士兵的身份是安杜阿拉姆·卡巴达 (Andualem Kabada)，21 岁，来自南部城市加特 (Kiryat Gat)；军方报告称，另一名士兵在同一事件中受重伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-saturday/0000018d-0879-d71c-ad9f-4bfb1dcb0000</guid></item><item><title>南非在国际法院传承曼德拉的遗产——也出于政治目的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/at-icj-south-africa-channels-mandelas-legacy-for-its-own-political-purposes/0000018d-0863-d71c-ad9f-4be37c4d0000</link><description>有几个原因可以解释南非为何向国际法院提交针对以色列的请愿书。其中一些涉及内部政治，另一些涉及区域和全球，但表明执政党有选择地利用纳尔逊·曼德拉的教义来分散人们对自身失败的注意力</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/at-icj-south-africa-channels-mandelas-legacy-for-its-own-political-purposes/0000018d-0863-d71c-ad9f-4be37c4d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准新监狱长，违反战时政府协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-to-vote-on-new-prison-chief-violating-wartime-govt-agreement/0000018d-0750-d832-a59d-17f75ef50000</link><description>政府投票并批准了本-格维尔的提议，任命其安全顾问科比·雅科比（Koby Yaakobi）为临时监狱专员。甘茨敦促内阁部长投票反对该提议，任命一位商定的候选人</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 13:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-to-vote-on-new-prison-chief-violating-wartime-govt-agreement/0000018d-0750-d832-a59d-17f75ef50000</guid></item><item><title>德国宣布决定代表以色列介入国际法院案件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/germany-announces-decision-to-intervene-on-israels-behalf-in-icj-case/0000018d-0787-dd07-a7df-cfff1f090000</link><description>德国联邦政府发言人加入了越来越多的以色列公众支持者行列，表示对以色列进行种族灭绝的指控“毫无根据”，德国打算在联合国最高法院的主听证会上作为第三方发言</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:56:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/germany-announces-decision-to-intervene-on-israels-behalf-in-icj-case/0000018d-0787-dd07-a7df-cfff1f090000</guid></item><item><title>冒雨寒冷，以色列举行24小时人质集会纪念哈马斯袭击100天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-rain-cold-israelis-mark-100-days-since-hamas-attack-with-daylong-rally-for-hostages/0000018d-076e-dd07-a7df-cf7ea6a40000</link><description>在特拉维夫所谓的人质广场，以色列人聚集在一起进行 24 小时的抗议、讨论和祈祷，为仍然被关押的 136 人祈祷，并对那些遇难者表示哀悼。早上 6 点 29 分，一名 DJ 播放了 10 月 7 日哈马斯猛攻开始时他在 Tribe of Nova 狂欢节上演奏的曲目</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-rain-cold-israelis-mark-100-days-since-hamas-attack-with-daylong-rally-for-hostages/0000018d-076e-dd07-a7df-cf7ea6a40000</guid></item><item><title>在华盛顿和纽约，巴勒斯坦人和以色列人和他们的美国支持者一起纪念以色列-哈马斯战争一百天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-and-israelis-their-u-s-supporters-mark-100-days-since-october-7/0000018d-0712-dd94-a9cd-47fe26910000</link><description>在华盛顿，亲巴勒斯坦抗议者批评拜登对以色列-哈马斯战争的政策，加沙人的家人讲述了他们的故事。在纽约市，亲以色列示威者与被释放的以色列人一起呼吁关注仍被扣押在加沙的数十名人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 11:12:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-and-israelis-their-u-s-supporters-mark-100-days-since-october-7/0000018d-0712-dd94-a9cd-47fe26910000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩总理与真主党保持一致：我们的命运与加沙息息相关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/lebanese-pm-toes-line-with-hezbollah-our-fate-tied-to-gaza/0000018d-0497-dd07-a7df-cfff4e0f0000</link><description>阿拉伯外交消息人士告诉《国土报》，要求真主党从边境撤退 40 公里并从南部撤军“缺乏任何操作逻辑”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 03:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/lebanese-pm-toes-line-with-hezbollah-our-fate-tied-to-gaza/0000018d-0497-dd07-a7df-cfff4e0f0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党导弹杀死两名以色列人后，以色列国防军深入黎巴嫩；格兰特警告约旦河西岸爆发冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article-live/idf-four-terrorists-attempting-to-infiltrate-israel-from-lebanon-killed-by-army/0000018d-0533-dd94-a9cd-47ff79b30000</link><description>人质家属在特拉维夫举行 24 小时集会，纪念被囚禁 100 天 ■ 以色列国防军称，四名恐怖分子在试图从黎巴嫩渗透以色列领土后被以色列军队打死 ■ 以色列国防军宣布一名士兵在加沙南部死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 03:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article-live/idf-four-terrorists-attempting-to-infiltrate-israel-from-lebanon-killed-by-army/0000018d-0533-dd94-a9cd-47ff79b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布周五在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-friday/0000018d-0469-dd07-a7df-cf7bcc5d0000</link><description>军士长。 (res.) 根据军方声明，24 岁的丹·瓦伊登鲍姆 (Dan Wajdenbaum) 被反坦克导弹炸死。此外，过去24小时内还有15名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 20:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/idf-releases-name-of-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-friday/0000018d-0469-dd07-a7df-cf7bcc5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报称哈马斯计划袭击海外目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-planned-attacks-on-targets-abroad-israeli-agencies-say/0000018d-0432-dd94-a9cd-46fe9dad0000</link><description>摩萨德和辛贝特表示，哈马斯在中东、非洲和欧洲策划恐怖袭击的阴谋被揭露后，三个欧洲国家被逮捕</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 20:02:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/hamas-planned-attacks-on-targets-abroad-israeli-agencies-say/0000018d-0432-dd94-a9cd-46fe9dad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议政府；抗议者封锁特拉维夫高速公路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-against-the-government-dozens-block-tel-aviv-highway/0000018d-03f3-dd07-a7df-cbfbeb930000</link><description>警察强行驱散耶路撒冷的反战抗议者。 “呼吁更换政府及其领导人并不是政治声明。这是一个实事求是、事实和道德的声明，”约拉姆·布斯基拉中校在特拉维夫集会上说</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 19:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-against-the-government-dozens-block-tel-aviv-highway/0000018d-03f3-dd07-a7df-cbfbeb930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列并未正式承认亚美尼亚种族灭绝，而是用它来嘲讽土耳其埃尔多安</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-doesnt-officially-recognize-the-armenian-genocide-but-uses-it-to-taunt-erdogan/0000018d-03cd-d832-a59d-17ff395e0000</link><description>据报道，作为以色列高级政治领导层对土耳其蓄意升级的一部分，以色列外交部长在一条推文中承认“土耳其犯下了亚美尼亚种族灭绝罪”</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 18:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-doesnt-officially-recognize-the-armenian-genocide-but-uses-it-to-taunt-erdogan/0000018d-03cd-d832-a59d-17ff395e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方下令向反内塔尼亚胡抗议组织者支付律师费</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ordered-to-pay-legal-fees-of-anti-netanyahu-protest-organizer/0000018d-03a8-dd07-a7df-cbfa13020000</link><description>在抗议者告诉人群警方正在创造侵犯民主权利的条件后，法官猛烈抨击警方逮捕了抗议者并禁止他进入抗议现场</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 16:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ordered-to-pay-legal-fees-of-anti-netanyahu-protest-organizer/0000018d-03a8-dd07-a7df-cbfa13020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在特拉维夫举行24小时大规模集会，要求释放加沙人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/24-hour-rally-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza-set-to-take-place-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-0369-d832-a59d-17ffd4a10000</link><description>&amp;#39;世界在哪里？决策者在哪里？恳求人质的母亲 ■ 播放法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的视频致辞 ■ 计划周一上午在全国范围内进行 100 分钟的声援罢工</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 16:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/24-hour-rally-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza-set-to-take-place-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-0369-d832-a59d-17ffd4a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女向正统男子提供非犹太三明治后，警方对她进行了询问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/police-question-israeli-woman-after-she-offered-non-kosher-sandwich-to-orthodox-man/0000018d-022b-dd07-a7df-cb7b91010000</link><description>事件发生前一天，学校经理被记录与一名查巴德特使对峙，查巴德特使在学校正门前搭建了一个佩戴 Tefillin（命匣）的架子。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/police-question-israeli-woman-after-she-offered-non-kosher-sandwich-to-orthodox-man/0000018d-022b-dd07-a7df-cb7b91010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级警官被指控性行为不端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</link><description>这名被指控违反信任罪的警官还被勒令离开车站一周。这名妇女正在嫌疑人监管的警察局中作为志愿者完成国民服役</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</guid></item></channel></rss>